ssions, one of which was recently introduced by Hegarty; while others\ngeneralize classical combinatorial games such as Nim and Wythoff Nim.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Jun 2012 05:22:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 11:00:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-11"}
